<h1>Obama's bid to defuse BP row in call to Cameron</h1>
<p>By <a href="/home/search.html?s=y&authornamef=Glen+Owen" class="author" rel="nofollow">Glen Owen</a><br/>
<span class="article-timestamp">
<strong>UPDATED:</strong>

05:09 EST, 13 June 2010

</span></p>
<div class="article-icon-links-container">
<ul class="article-icon-links cleared">
<li class="first">
<a class="comments-link" href="/money/news/article-1695861/Obamas-bid-to-defuse-BP-row-in-call-to-Cameron.html#comments" rel="nofollow">
<span class="icon"></span><span class="linktext">Comments (<span class="readerCommentNo" rel="1695861">0</span>)</span>
</a>
</li>
<li id="shareLink" class=" gr3ox">
<a class="js-sl share-link" href="#socialLinks">
